title: our summer 2022 bucket lists

description:
Brooke and Danielle are getting into the SUMMER MOOD this week!  The gals are sharing what is on their bucket list for this summer and some summer goals they have.  Tune in to get some inspiration on what to do this summer to avoid boredom, and explore your own city/town.   Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!
